  "title": "What is Mathematics?  What is a proof?  Why do we prove things?",
  "body": " What is Mathematics? What is a proof? Why do we prove things?  What happens next? Does it always work? How many are there? Why does it work? What if we tried this instead?  Questions such as these are at the heart of mathematics, where we seek to identify, understand, and explain patterns.  "
